2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with wireless sensor networks, which is a sub-domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the entropy change analysis of the algorithm, which is a concept from information theory. 
4. cs.SE (Software Engineering) - The paper may also fall under the category of software engineering as it evaluates the performance of the algorithm and suggests possible solutions for its weaknesses. 
5. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper may also have implications for the societal impact of wireless sensor networks and their security.
